lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c380abd2e81ee1783c26f4a7e4525ac0b9f65fbf","tid":361682,"uid":60982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"王老吉無咁好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2700a323faa6e18e96237d49e9044b19c2135d52","tid":361682,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加多寶 先係真正王老吉.<br />\n點都會買加多寶, 唔會買王老吉.</blockquote><br />\n加多寶打江山<br />\n王老吉享成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細過飲開王老吉以為先係正版<br />\n人大左無聊走去google下<br />\n先知加多寶先係堅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但有無人覺得而家甜左好多？之前涼茶味濃啲"},{"pid":"5c2ad9056e8b72b8bd148f649e4a108967c3244f","tid":361682,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>加多寶 先係真正王老吉.<br />\n點都會買加多寶, 唔會買王老吉.</blockquote><br />\n加多寶打江山<br />\n王老吉享成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細過飲開王老吉以為先係正版<br />\n人大左無聊走去google下<br />\n先知加多寶先係堅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但有無人覺得而家甜左好多？之前涼茶味濃啲</blockquote><br />\n細個果陣的確叫王老吉 廣藥租左王老吉既名比依家既加多寶用黎整鋁罐版 綠色紙盒裝就廣藥自己整返 果陣好似都叨光叨到每年賣10億包<br />\n<br />\n後尾加多寶做大左 廣藥諗住痴住王老吉個市場拎返黎自己搞 所以反左面"},{"pid":"970fcded16fbb8c5b67593679693a84e811639b3","tid":361682,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"律師真係大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4183638b264f32377edfd5ab303ad620d1a045c1","tid":361682,"uid":17081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/aaa_203824362558d3b0b04f511-800x450.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Faaa_203824362558d3b0b04f511-800x450.png&h=2e201ca5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}